column1: # Name: Mean age at first marriage, male

# Definition: The mean age at first marriage is the mean age of men or women at first marriage if subject throughout their lives to the age-specific marriage rates of first marriages only in a given year.
# Source: United Nations, World Fertility Report, 2012
# Data from the No Ceilings project: http://noceilings.org
# For more about the data, please visit http://noceilings.org/data
